snippet.title: The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos - Gameplay Walkthrough Part 1 (No Commentary, PC)
snippet.description:
Checking out this new dungeon crawler. It's fun and has you think and strategize a lot but man the music cuts out all the time. Wish they could put it on loop or something. Idk something to fix in future updates. Enjoy

►NOTE - Thanks to Kris of Future Friend Games for the game!
